description: These aromatic prawn skewers make a quick and easy starter or light lunch.
name: Coconut Chilli Prawn Skewers Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Heat the BBQ to the highest setting. Thread the prawns onto the skewers and brush with marinade. Grill for 2 minutes on each side or until cooked through. Serve with fresh chopped coriander and coconut flakes scattered on top.
